social_posts.post_text: Happy birthday hubs. Thank you for making my world a little brighter. May every new chapter be better than our last. Cheers to you today and always! I love you so much. ❤️ @tommyteeee

If I have learned anything this year, it’s that I won’t always be ready for what life has to throw at me. I’ve experienced the highest of highs and lowest of lows and will forever be grateful for those who kept my head up. But as one door opens and another closes, I will move forward with the knowledge that tomorrow is never promised - so love and appreciate the people in your life and focus on what’s important. Don’t postpone enjoyment.

On that note: Miami, thank you for being my whole life for the last 34 years. But onto new horizons and adventures with the love of my life! Farewell to my hometown - see you in #2023, Denver. 🚙💨❄️👩🏼‍🦰❤️🐶👨🏼‍🦲🏔️✨
